'''Beyoncé Knowles''' bu onye [[United States of Amerika|Amerikạ]] nwayị na bụ abụ. Ha muru ya na ogẹ September 4 1981 na Houston, nor na Texas ime ọbọdọ Amerikạ. Ngbe o dị ntakiri o nọr na ébé há na kuzi i gbá nkwạ na i gwu nkwạ. O bụ onye dim-kpạ maka o nọrọ na, ötü ndi umụ nwanyị nägwü nkwa há na kpo Destiny's child. Na uwa nilé, hë rẹrẹ nkwa rúrú ndẹ 50.

== Ndụ ya mbu ==
Na Houston, Texas ébé há mụrụ Knowles, o bụ ádá Matthew Knowles, onye ahia égwú, na Tina Beyincé, onye na dọr ákwạ ná onye na edozi isi. Nna Knowles bu onye [[African American]] na mma ya bu onye [[ndi Louisiana Creole]] ([[African American]], [[Diạlạ Amerika]], na [[France|French]]) ébé ndi Creole shi nọr na obodo [[Louisiana]], ime [[Amerika]]. Ha gụrụ Knowles mgbe ha goziri ya na ụlọ ụka, Aha ya shi aha mma ya ukwu maka ndi Beyincé nwere nwoko ntakiri i gi were aha nké.

